subject: Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Playing with short rest, Georgia stunned Mississippi State, 64-60, to advance to Sunday’s final against Arkansas. The Razorbacks upset No. 4 Tennessee, 92-91, earlier in the day.
